snippet.title: Google Research
snippet.description: Welcome to the official YouTube channel for Google Research. Explore video content that tackles state of the art research across Google like ML/AI, robotics, theory and algorithms, quantum computing, health, bioscience, and much more. Learn about the latest publications, research breakthroughs and the people behind them.
